This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses brain-inspired learning mechanisms and spiking neural networks. It may also belong to cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) as it incorporates emerging nanoscale resistive non-volatile memory devices. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) as it proposes a novel processing architecture and neuron circuits. The paper also discusses the use of CMOS technology, which could place it under cs.EM (Embedded Systems) or cs.CE (Computer Engineering).
